 />1.How do you currently incorporate physical activity into your daily routine?<br />2.What are some barriers that prevent you from meeting the recommended amount of weekly physical activity?<br />3.What types of physical activities do you enjoy doing, and how do they benefit your overall health?<br />4.How can workplaces and communities encourage more physical activity among their members?<br />5.How do you prioritize physical activity in your busy schedule and make time for it?<br /><br />P.S.<br />1.參加三次後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />2.請帶著開放與熱情來參加自由的全英文會話聚會~<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=12531">Danny Lin</a> — Wed Mar 01, 2023 11:46 pm</p><hr />
